 If Jane bought 40 eggs on May 9th, 2017, then she ate one per day, so she ate 40 eggs in 40 days. So the last day she ate an egg is 40 days after May 9th, 2017, which is June 17th, 2017. Today is 1 day after June 17th, 2017, which is June 18th, 2017. So the answer is 6/18/2017.

Q: On
Answer 6/18/2017 expected 06/18/2017
