Q: Jane thought today is 3/11/2002, but today is in fact Mar 12, which is 1 day later. What is the date one year ago from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If today is 3/11/2002, then today is 1 day later than 3/11/2002, which is 3/12/2002. One year ago from today is 1 year in the past of today, which is 3/12/2001. So the answer is 3/12/2001.

Q: Today
Answer 3/12/2001 expected 03/12/2001
Total examples: 43 Correct answers: 24
Q: Today's meeting is rescheduled to 11 am tomorrow, 10/16/1924. What is the date a month ago in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If today's meeting is rescheduled to 11 am tomorrow, then today is 10/16/1924. One month ago from today is 1 month in the past of today, which is 9/16/1924. So the answer is 9/16/1924.

Q: Today
Answer 9/16/1924 expected 09/15/1924
Total examples: 44 Correct answers: 24
Q: Jane was born on the last day of Feburary in 2001. Today is her 16-year-old birthday. What is the date one year ago from today in MM/DD/YYYY?
A:
 If today is her 16-year-old birthday, then today is 02/28/2017. One year ago from today is 1 year in the past of today, which is 02/28/2016. So the answer is 02/28/2016.

Q: Today
Answer 02/28/2016 expected 02/28/2016
